text: Alan Eduardovich Gagloyev (; ; born 6 February 1981) is a South Ossetian politician and intelligence officer. He is the 5th and current president of South Ossetia since May 24, 2022. He is the current chairman of the Nykhaz party since February 2020. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of South Ossetia Category:Current national leaders
